  "detailed_description": "<h1>Brazilian month of suicide prevention</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1726050/extras/eb33644371626082c412b253bcb06691.avif?t=1678399449\" width=594 height=320 /></span><br>Neon Depth was released in September, which in Brazil is the month of suicide prevention. All the money raised this month will be donated and dedicated to the cause that affects many people's lives, mental health.</p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1726050/extras/3aa311ed0c0f979b77b93dd1c1a27e01.poster.avif?t=1678399449\" width=594 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1726050/extras/3aa311ed0c0f979b77b93dd1c1a27e01.webm?t=1678399449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1726050/extras/3aa311ed0c0f979b77b93dd1c1a27e01.mp4?t=1678399449\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Neon Depth is a puzzle game with platform elements, in which to progress mistakes must be made.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1726050/extras/192c58997a5a21c272aa8e6d59a49476.poster.avif?t=1678399449\" width=594 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1726050/extras/192c58997a5a21c272aa8e6d59a49476.webm?t=1678399449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1726050/extras/192c58997a5a21c272aa8e6d59a49476.mp4?t=1678399449\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>A block appears where you failed, which can help you on your next attempt.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1726050/extras/8aeefaf59f8678e9d99751e1359c81c0.poster.avif?t=1678399449\" width=594 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1726050/extras/8aeefaf59f8678e9d99751e1359c81c0.webm?t=1678399449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1726050/extras/8aeefaf59f8678e9d99751e1359c81c0.mp4?t=1678399449\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Some blocks have different colors and functions, and it is up to the player to identify which one should be used in each situation.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1726050/extras/c50365b133b09fb07bd779c240fe5a95.poster.avif?t=1678399449\" width=594 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1726050/extras/c50365b133b09fb07bd779c240fe5a95.webm?t=1678399449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1726050/extras/c50365b133b09fb07bd779c240fe5a95.mp4?t=1678399449\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>By placing a block in an unwanted location, the player is able to destroy it to reverse his mistake.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1726050/extras/22d4a9f5a3c2801759cbb124c9eb5d6b.poster.avif?t=1678399449\" width=594 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1726050/extras/22d4a9f5a3c2801759cbb124c9eb5d6b.webm?t=1678399449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1726050/extras/22d4a9f5a3c2801759cbb124c9eb5d6b.mp4?t=1678399449\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Be part of this journey about overcoming, full of analogies and reflections on learning how to move forward.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <strong> Main Features</strong>  </h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong> Challenging yet satisfying puzzles </strong><br></li><li> <strong> Be part of an inspiring narrative about accepting mistakes and moving forward </strong><br></li><li><strong>Minimalist retro design inspired by the 90's arcades</strong><br></li><li> <strong> Platform sections </strong><br></li><li> <strong> Atmospheric soundtrack </strong></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1726050/extras/3aa311ed0c0f979b77b93dd1c1a27e01.poster.avif?t=1678399449\" width=594 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1726050/extras/3aa311ed0c0f979b77b93dd1c1a27e01.webm?t=1678399449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1726050/extras/3aa311ed0c0f979b77b93dd1c1a27e01.mp4?t=1678399449\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Neon Depth is a puzzle game with platform elements, in which to progress mistakes must be made.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1726050/extras/192c58997a5a21c272aa8e6d59a49476.poster.avif?t=1678399449\" width=594 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1726050/extras/192c58997a5a21c272aa8e6d59a49476.webm?t=1678399449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1726050/extras/192c58997a5a21c272aa8e6d59a49476.mp4?t=1678399449\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>A block appears where you failed, which can help you on your next attempt.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1726050/extras/8aeefaf59f8678e9d99751e1359c81c0.poster.avif?t=1678399449\" width=594 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1726050/extras/8aeefaf59f8678e9d99751e1359c81c0.webm?t=1678399449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1726050/extras/8aeefaf59f8